Class Farmer

java.lang.Object
Farmer
Direct Known Subclasses:
DistinguishedFarmer, LegendaryFarmer, RegisteredFarmer
public class Farmer extends Object
This class represents the details of the farmer (the player) and. the player themselves. It contains the current coins of the player, their farmer level and experience and, the current day of the game. A Farmer object represent the player and its current attributes. There can only be one player.
